            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add your<strong> white long grain rice</strong>, <strong>tomato stock </strong>and <strong>half</strong> the<strong> chopped chilli </strong>(can't handle the heat? Go easy!) to the pan and bring to the boil over a high heat</p><p>Once boiling, reduce the heat to very low and cook, covered, for 12-15 min or until all the water has absorbed and the rice is cooked – this is your <strong>spicy rice</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-4-1713869559145-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
