            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>peri peri free range chicken</strong> with the <strong>spicy rice</strong> and<strong> lemony salad </strong>to the side</p><p>Garnish with a <strong>remaining</strong> <strong>lemon wedge</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
